<p>She was born in Ankara in 1982. After TED Ankara College, she studied Computer Engineering at Bilkent University and got her MA degree from Department of Industrial Engineering at METU. She has been working as consultant and project manager in various technology companies for more than 10 years. She was a volunteer, member of board of trustees, and member of board of directors at Community Volunteers Foundation. She is one of the founding members of SEN DE GEL. She is married and has two children.</p>